            <title>[LU-13188] add -q option to &apos;lctl set_param&apos; to quiet output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13188</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add a &apos;&lt;tt&gt;-q&lt;/tt&gt;&apos; option to &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl set_param&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; so that it will set parameters without printing the parameter name and value afterward.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
